'''Calanques de Piana''' ({{lang-co|'''E Calanche di Piana'''}}) are [[Corsica]]n [[calanque]]s located in [[Piana]], between [[Ajaccio]] and [[Calvi, Haute-Corse|Calvi]], in the gulf of [[Porto (Corsica)|Porto]]. It is part of a UNESCO World Heritage Site named "Gulf of Porto: Calanche of Piana, [[Corsica#Ecology|Gulf of Girolata]], [[Scandola Nature Reserve|Scandola Reserve]]".

